# StudySync (Backend) âš™ï¸ğŸ“š

## ğŸ§  Overview
StudySync is a productivity API built with **Node.js + Express + MongoDB**.
It supports authentication with **JWT** and provides endpoints for:
- Tasks management
- Study sessions tracking
- Wellness logging (water / exercise / sleep)
- Dashboard summaries (quick overview of everything)

This repository contains the **back-end** portion of the MERN stack project â€” built with **Express**, **Mongoose**, and connected to MongoDB.

