âœ¨ Key Features
ğŸ” Authentication (JWT)

Sign Up / Sign In

Protected routes using Authorization: Bearer <token>

User info routes (current user)

Note: Your ERD includes email, but the current backend may not store it yet.
If you want email support, add email to the User model + update auth controller.

âœ… Tasks API

Create tasks with title + due date

Update tasks

Delete tasks

Mark tasks complete

Fetch tasks per user

â±ï¸ Study Sessions API

Save sessions (start/end time)

View study history

Delete sessions

Dashboard totals

ğŸ’§ Wellness Logs API

Track daily wellness habits:

water glasses

exercise minutes

sleep hours

View wellness history

Update one log per day (upsert pattern)

ğŸ¨ Dashboard Summary

One endpoint that returns:

tasks totals (completed/remaining)

total study minutes/hours

latest wellness log

ğŸ§© API Routes
ğŸ” Auth

POST /auth/sign-up

POST /auth/sign-in

Example body:

{
  "username": "test",
  "password": "1234"
}

ğŸ‘¤ Users (Protected)

GET /users

GET /users/current-user

GET /users/:id

Optional improvement:

PUT /users/current-user (to allow profile editing from frontend)

âœ… Tasks (Protected)

Base: /tasks

GET /tasks

POST /tasks

PUT /tasks/:id

DELETE /tasks/:id

Example:

{
  "title": "Finish report",
  "description": "Write final section",
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31",
  "priority": "high",
  "completed": false
}

â±ï¸ Study Sessions (Protected)

Base: /studySessions

GET /studySessions

POST /studySessions

DELETE /studySessions/:id

Example:

{
  "startTime": "2025-12-27T10:00:00.000Z",
  "endTime": "2025-12-27T11:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "completed"
}

ğŸ’§ Wellness Logs (Protected)

Base: /wellnessLogs

GET /wellnessLogs

POST /wellnessLogs

DELETE /wellnessLogs/:id

Example:

{
  "date": "2025-12-27",
  "waterGlasses": 6,
  "exerciseMinutes": 20,
  "sleepHours": 7
}

ğŸ“Š Dashboard (Protected)

GET /dashboard

Example response:

{
  "tasks": { "total": 4, "completed": 1 },
  "study": { "totalMinutes": 210, "totalHours": 3.5 },
  "wellness": {
    "date": "2025-12-27T00:00:00.000Z",
    "waterGlasses": 6,
    "exerciseMinutes": 20,
    "sleepHours": 7
  }
}

